snippet.title: original song: “cell”
snippet.description:
Lyrics:

It’s not easy for me, it’s not easy for you to see 
I can’t just move on like you do
And I’m so angry, not at him but at me
For believing your words to be true
When you don’t know me and I don’t know you 
You don’t know me I don’t know you 
You don’t know me I don’t know you 

And why am always trying to change people?
When I can’t change people
Trying to fix the past again 
There’s plenty of fish in the sea, but I can’t see them
There’s something pulling me towards him
Something pulling me towards him 
Something pulling me towards him 

And I need to get out of this place
 But I don’t know how 
I want to leave but something makes me stay 
I feel like I’m in a cell
I feel like I’m in a cell
I feel like I’m in a cell


—————————————

Love you guys!!❤️
